item.title: CVE-2017-3751|2024-08-05T14:39:40.626Z -- lenovo%20group%20ltd. -- thinkpad%20compact%20usb%20keyboard%20with%20trackpoint%20driver
item.description: An unquoted service path vulnerability was identified in the driver for the ThinkPad Compact USB Keyboard with TrackPoint versions earlier than 1.5.5.0. This could allow an attacker with local privileges to execute code with administrative privileges.
